title: Grateful Dead Live at Radio City Music Hall on 1980-10-29
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi DR-1/Dolby B) -> Sound Devices 744T (24bit/96k) -> Adobe Audition v1.5 -> Samplitude Professional v10.21 -> FLAC/16
description:
Set 1

Dire Wolf, On The Road Again, It Must Have Been The Roses, The Race is On, Bird Song, Heaven Help The Fool, Ain't No Lie-> Ripple

Set 2

Feel Like A Stranger-> Franklin's Tower, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Candyman-> Little Red Rooster, Tennessee Jed, Looks Like Rain, Althea-> The Music Never Stopped

Set 3

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider-> Estimated Prophet-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Black Peter-> Sugar Magnolia, E: U.S. Blues

First Set Acoustic
